{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "第二回\"拳头对拳头\"叙述丁喜与小马在屋内饮酒，丁喜旋开旗杆顶端，取出谭道托镖的七十二颗明珠，价值百万两。丁喜计划将贼赃变卖，以接济乱石岗、青风山等处死于五犬旗下的孤寡。二人前往保定府寻找专收贼赃的首富张金鼎。张金鼎带着两名花衣镖客到场，丁喜以四万铜钱的荒唐价格成交，白打了张金鼎三拳出气后主动认输。花衣镖客随即亮明身份——一人是\"神拳小诸葛\"邓定侯，另一人是中原镖局第一高手\"乾坤笔\"西门胜。文中借此介绍开花五犬旗下五大镖局首领：司马长青、邓定侯、归东景、姜新、西门胜。丁喜提出\"文打\"之法，以打张金鼎为赌，趁机痛殴张金鼎后认输。小马不服，挥拳向西门胜，却被邓定侯拦住，最终以\"拳头对拳头\"收束全章，留下悬念。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你的真气真足。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你知不知道这旗杆里藏着什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你也不知道我为什么要你抢这面旗子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你能不能少用嘴吹气，多用脑袋想想。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "可是大哥你究竟要我想什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "每件事你都可以想，想通了之后再去做。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我用不着去想，反正大哥你要我去干什么，我就去干什么！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我想不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你想不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "这旗杆既不太粗，又不太长，我实在想不出里面能藏多少值钱的东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "要找一颗这样的珍珠也许还不太难，可是七十二颗同样的……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "看来谭道这个人，虽然心狠手辣，倒还真有点本事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "谭道？是不是那个专会刮皮的狗官谭道？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "这些珠子是他的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "是他特别买来的，送给他京城里的靠山作寿礼的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个老上八蛋，我早就想宰了他，亏他妈的邓定侯还自命英雄，居然肯替这种龟孙子做走狗！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "保镖的眼睛里只有两种人，一种是顾客，一种是强盛，强盗永远该死，顾客永远是对的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "就算这顾客是乌龟王八，也都是对的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "不管这强盗是哪种强盗，在他们眼里都该死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "以你看，这些珍珠可以值多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我看不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "一百万两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "一百万两银子？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "只不过这是贼赃，他们若急着卖，最多只卖六成。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我们是不是急着要卖？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "不但要急着卖，而且一定要现钱。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "乱石岗的沙家七兄弟都死在五犬旗下，留下的满门孤寡，还有青风山和西河十八寨的兄弟，就算他是罪有应得，他们的孤儿寡妇并没有罪。这些女人孩子都有权活下去，要活下去，就得有饭吃，要有饭，就得要银子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "一百万两，六成，是不是六十万两？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这次你总算没有算错。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "六十万两银子，要我一箱箱地搬也得搬老半天，江湖中有谁能一下子于就搬出这么多银子来，买这批烫手的货？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "保定府是个大地方，振威的镖局就在保定，城里城外，说不走到处都有他们的耳目",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "那地方他们的狗腿子实在不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "那么你想，我为什么别的地方不去，偏偏要到保定来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我想不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你真的想不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "大哥既然已想出来了，为什么还要我想？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为我要抽出你几条懒筋，再拔出你几根懒骨头，治好你的懒病。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你知不知道张金鼎这个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你知不知道张金鼎是靠什么发财起家的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "有种人虽然不自己动手去抢，却比强盗的心更黑，别人卖了命抢来的货，他三文不值二文地买下来，一转手至少就可以赚个对开对利。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你说的是不是那些专收贼脏的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "张金鼎本来就是这种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "现在他还是这种人，只不过现在他的胃口大了，小一点儿的买卖，他已看不上眼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "咱们到保定府来，为的就是要找他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "这种人简直他妈的不是人，大哥居然要来找他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "他来找的不是我，是我的银子。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "你就是那姓张的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你就是那个愤怒的小马？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "我怎么知道你是不是真的张金鼎？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你应该看得出，除了我之外，谁有我这一身肉？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "你这一身肥肉是从哪里来的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "当然是从你们这些人身上来的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "莫忘记我是你大哥请来的客人，你若打了我，就等于打你大哥的脸。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "现在我们是不是已经可以进来了，请说。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "要进来，也只准你一个人进来。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你们有两个人，我当然也得两个人进去，我做买卖，一向公平交易。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "你自己呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我这个人根本不能算是个人，这是你自己刚才说的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "既然连张老板自己都不把自己当做人，你又何必生气？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我只不过在奇怪，这世上为什么总会有些人不喜欢做人呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为这年头只有做人难，无论做牛做猪做狗，都比做人容易。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "这就是你要卖给我的货？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "若不是这样的货，我们岂敢劳动张老板的大驾？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你想卖多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "一百万两。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "一百万两？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "你是在说话，还是在放屁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我只不过是在做生意，漫天要价，落地还钱，做生意本来都是这样子的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "我们可不是生意人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "张老板若喜欢讨价还价，我可以奉陪。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我最多只能出两万。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "九十九万。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "三万。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "九十八万。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "四万。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "好，我卖了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "我是个很知足的人，知足常乐。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你知不知道我出的四万，是四万什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "难道不是四万两银子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "speaker_name": "张金鼎",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "是四万个铜钱。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "四万个铜钱我也卖了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "莫说还有四万个铜钱，就算张老板一文不给，我也卖了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我大哥肯卖，我可不肯。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你大哥肯，你也得肯。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你一定要问为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为我怕打架。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你怕跟这个人打架？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "象张老板这样的角色，就算来上七八百个，要打架我还是随时可以奉陪的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "那么你怕跟谁打架？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你真的看不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我看不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "花衣镖客",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我看得出。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你？你他妈的看出了什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "花衣镖客",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我至少已看出了一件事。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "花衣镖客",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "讨人喜欢的丁喜实在不愧是黑道上的第一号智多星，愤怒的小马却实在是他妈的一个大草包。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "你是什么东西？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "花衣镖客",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你还看不出？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "我只看出了你既不是东西，也不是人，最多只不过是他妈的一条白狗。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "果然不错，果然是小猪哥。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "但我却看错了你，你倒不是大草包，最多只不过是条小驴子而已。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你真的怕打架？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "真的，只可惜这场架看来已非打不可。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "那你为什么要拉住我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为现在还没有到开始的时候。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "要等到什么时候？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我们至少得等西门大镖头先脱下戏服来再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "想不到你居然也认出了我。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "我倒没有认出你，只不过认出了你身上这对乾坤笔而已。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "你就是西门胜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "现在是不是已到了开始打架的时候？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "你说怎么打？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "打架只有一种打法。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "哪种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "打到对方躺下去，再也爬不起来时为止。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "好，这种打法正对了我的口味。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "这种打法却不对你大哥的口味。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "我找的不是你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "据我所知，打架的法子有两种，一种是文打，一种是武打。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你想文打？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "象西门大镖头这种有身份的人，总不能象两条狗一样咬来咬去吧。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "文打怎么打？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "我说出来，你肯答应？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "对付阁下这样的人，无论怎么打都是一样。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "好，既然如此，我们就这么样打。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你怎么能打他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "这就是我的打法，我们谁先把这位张老板打得躺下去，再也爬不起来，谁就胜了，但却只准用拳头打。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "哪有这种打法！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "你说过，无论我要怎么打，你都答应，你若不想败，马上跟我一样打。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_zhang_jin_ding",
      "text": "你还爬不爬得起来？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "他已爬不起来，你就算输了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你还不认输？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "我认输，我本来就准备认输的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "西门胜",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "输了为什么还要笑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xi_men_sheng",
      "text": "因为我白打了这乌龟三拳，气已出了一半。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你真的本来就准备认输？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "西门胜战无不胜，邓定侯神拳无敌，就凭我们兄弟，能击败人家的机会实在不多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "只要有一分机会，我们也得——",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "何况，就算我们能击败他们，我们自己也并没有什么好处，就算还没有被打得头破血流，也一定已精疲力竭，哪里还能对付外面的那些人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_xi",
      "speaker_name": "丁喜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "所以到头来我们还是非输不可，既然非输不可，为什么不输得漂亮些？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_ding_xi",
      "text": "你认输，我可不认输。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 564,
      "line_end": 564
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "text": "闪开，我找的不是你。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "现在已轮到我，你不找我也不行。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_deng_ding_hou",
      "speaker_name": "邓定侯",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我用的也是拳头，我们正好拳头对拳头。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    }
